metadata.name: anahita
metadata.description:
She is one of the Iranian-Aryan goddesses. He is worshiped by Ahura Mazda and Zoroaster and has great value and prestige. Anahita is in charge of guarding all the waters of the world.
From the rain. Clouds of hail and wind gain power
And goes to confront his enemies
He shines like the stars
I think Anahita is attractive, beautiful and powerful
